Author: setpass
Title: ğŸ”¥[ANN][ICO] Profede â€” Professional Decentralization ğŸ”¥
Body: In the current billionaire professional market (recruiting and social selling), too much money goes to the intermediaries and there is little left for professionals and businesses. Profede is using blockchain to bypass the intermediaries in the professional world and create a direct connection between professionals and businesses. On the Profede Professional Protocol, professionals control their personal data and get paid each time businesses access it to offer them a uniquely targeted job offer, a commercial offer or a specific business proposal. Profede brings essential value to professionals and businesses by making data valuable and eliminating intermediaries
